<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="keywords" content="美眉图库-基于nodejs开发-https://github.com/tsq/girl-gallery"/><meta name="description" content="美眉图片"/>
    <title>美眉图库</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="asset/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            padding-top: 60px;
            background: #222;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top" role="navigation">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="navbar-header">
            <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
                <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            </button>
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="https://github.com/tsq/girl-gallery" target="_blank">本网站是作者学习nodejs技术的练习作品,无任何商业目的,纯属个人娱乐,如有冒犯请多包含!网站图片来自'22MM图库',想看更多图片,可以百度搜索前往观看。另外,本项目开源,点击此链接即可访问github库地址。</a>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-collapse collapse">
            <!--            <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                            <li><a href="#">Dashboard</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Settings</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Profile</a></li>
